{"id":216,"parent_id":193,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":216,"title":"Joshua 23","subtitle":"","short_title":"Josh.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 23"],[".studySummary",["i","Joshua exhorts Israel to be courageous, keep the commandments, love the Lord, and neither marry among nor cleave unto the remnants of the Canaanites who remain in the land—When the children of Israel serve other gods, they will be cursed and dispossessed."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.1","order":"02.07.023.18962"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass a long time after that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had given",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"rest"],"unto Israel from all their enemies round about, that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Joshua"],"waxed old",["i","and"],"stricken in age."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.2","order":"02.07.023.18963"},["b","2"],"And Joshua called for all Israel,",["i","and"],"for their elders, and for their heads, and for their judges, and for their officers, and said unto them, I am old",["i","and"],"stricken in age:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.3","order":"02.07.023.18964"},["b","3"],"And ye have seen all that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God hath done unto all these nations because of you; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God",["i","is"],"he that hath fought for you."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.4","order":"02.07.023.18965"},["b","4"],"Behold, I have divided unto you by lot these nations that remain, to be an inheritance for your tribes, from Jordan, with all the nations that I have cut off, even unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"great sea"],"westward."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.5","order":"02.07.023.18966"},["b","5"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"expel"],"them from before you, and drive them from out of your sight; and ye shall possess their land, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God hath promised unto you."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.6","order":"02.07.023.18967"},["b","6"],"Be ye therefore very",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"courageous"],"to keep and to do all that is written in the book of the law of Moses, that ye turn not aside therefrom",["i","to"],"the right hand or",["i","to"],"the left;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.7","order":"02.07.023.18968"},["b","7"],"That ye come not among these nations, these that remain among you; neither make mention of the name of their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"gods"],", nor cause to swear",["i","by them,"],"neither serve them, nor bow yourselves unto them:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.8","order":"02.07.023.18969"},["b","8"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"cleave"],"unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, as ye have done unto this day."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.9","order":"02.07.023.18970"},["b","9"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath driven out from before you great nations and strong: but",["i","as for"],"you, no man hath been able to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"stand"],"before you unto this day."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.10","order":"02.07.023.18971"},["b","10"],"One man of you shall chase a thousand: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, he",["i","it is"],"that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"fighteth"],"for you, as he hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"promised"],"you."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.11","order":"02.07.023.18972"},["b","11"],"Take good heed therefore unto yourselves, that ye love the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.12","order":"02.07.023.18973"},["b","12"],"Else if ye do in any wise go back, and cleave unto the remnant of these nations,",["i","even"],"these that remain among you, and shall make",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"marriages"],"with them, and go in unto them, and they to you:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.13","order":"02.07.023.18974"},["b","13"],"Know for a certainty that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God will no more drive out",["i","any of"],"these nations from before you; but they shall be snares and traps unto you, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"scourges"],"in your sides, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"thorns"],"in your eyes, until ye",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"perish"],"from off this good land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God hath given you."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.14","order":"02.07.023.18975"},["b","14"],"And, behold, this day I",["i","am"],"going the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"way"],"of all the earth: and ye know in all your hearts and in all your souls, that not one thing hath failed of all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"good"],"things which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God spake concerning you; all are come to pass unto you,",["i","and"],"not one thing hath failed thereof."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.15","order":"02.07.023.18976"},["b","15"],"Therefore it shall come to pass,",["i","that"],"as all good things are come upon you, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"promised"],"you; so shall the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"bring upon you all evil things, until he have destroyed you from off this good land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God hath given you."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.16","order":"02.07.023.18977"},["b","16"],"When ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"transgressed"],"the covenant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, which he commanded you, and have gone and served other gods, and bowed yourselves to them; then shall the anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"be kindled against you, and ye shall perish quickly from off the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"good"],"land which he hath given unto you."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.1a","order":"02.07.023.18978"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/22.4"},"Josh. 22:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.1b","order":"02.07.023.18980"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/13.1"},"Josh. 13:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.4a","order":"02.07.023.18982"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/15.12"},"Josh. 15:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.5a","order":"02.07.023.18984"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.37.33-38"},"D&C 98:37 (33–38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.6a","order":"02.07.023.18986"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courage"},"TG Courage"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.7a","order":"02.07.023.18988"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.13"},"Ex. 23:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.8a","order":"02.07.023.18990"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/18.6"},"2 Kgs. 18:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.5"},"Jacob 6:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.25"},"Hel. 4:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.19"},"D&C 11:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.9a","order":"02.07.023.18992"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/21.44"},"Josh. 21:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.10a","order":"02.07.023.18994"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/20.4"},"Deut. 20:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.10b","order":"02.07.023.18996"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promise"},"TG Promise"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.12a","order":"02.07.023.18998"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-interfaith"},"TG Marriage, Interfaith"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.13a","order":"02.07.023.19000"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/1.27.27-36"},"Judg. 1:27 (27–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.13b","order":"02.07.023.19002"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/33.55"},"Num. 33:55"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/28.24"},"Ezek. 28:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.24"},"1 Ne. 2:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.28.27-28"},"3 Ne. 20:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.13c","order":"02.07.023.19004"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.21.20-21"},"1 Ne. 2:21 (20–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.14a","order":"02.07.023.19006"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/2.2"},"1 Kgs. 2:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/1.14"},"2 Ne. 1:14"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death"},"TG Death"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.14b","order":"02.07.023.19008"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/82.10"},"D&C 82:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.15a","order":"02.07.023.19010"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/21.45"},"Josh. 21:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.16a","order":"02.07.023.19012"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.2"},"Deut. 17:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.15"},"D&C 1:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.6.6-8"},"3:6 (6–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/54.4.3-6"},"54:4 (3–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/104.52"},"104:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.16b","order":"02.07.023.19014"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/14.15"},"1 Kgs. 14:15"],"."]]}
